---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav/index.astro';
import SkipToContent from '../components/SkipToContent/index.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/Base.astro';

import { GLOBALS } from '../constants.js';

import '../assets/css/pages/triangle.css';

import customer from '../assets/images/piramid/customer.jpg';
import eMusk from '../assets/images/piramid/e-musk.jpg';
import ligMa from '../assets/images/piramid/ligma.jpg';
import mScott from '../assets/images/piramid/m-scott.jpg';
import mrCreature from '../assets/images/piramid/mr-creature.jpg';
import richHero from '../assets/images/piramid/rich1.png';

// eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-magic-numbers
const IMAGE_WIDTHS = [128, 256, 512, 768, richHero.width];
---
<BaseLayout
	htmlTitle={['QuickRichClub', ...GLOBALS.title]}
	title="QuickRichClub"
	description="Welcome to QuickRichClub!"
	url="/triangle"
	tags={['easter egg', 'joke', ...GLOBALS.tags]}
>
	<SkipToContent slot="header" />
	<SiteNav slot="header" />

	<h1>Welcome to QuickRichClub!</h1>

	<section id="hero">
		<Image
			src={richHero}
			alt="A man with a happy face and his mouth open, holding a fist in front of his body. He is confident, he is strong, he is making money baby!"
			loading="lazy"
			widths={IMAGE_WIDTHS}
			sizes={`(max-width: 360px) 128px, (max-width: 720px) 256px, (max-width: 1280px) 512px, (max-width: 2160px) 768px ${richHero.width}px`}
			quality={75}
		/>

		<p>
			Ready to swim in cash? Join QuickRichClub, where everyone can &ldquo;get rich quick&rdquo;! ðŸ’¸
			<small class="tiny-text">(terms and conditions apply, mainly to everyone except you)</small>
		</p>

		<form method="get" action="#">
			<input
				id="email"
				name="email"
				type="email"
				placeholder="Enter your email here"
				aria-label="Enter your email here"
				required
			/>
			<button type="submit">Join now!</button>
		</form>
	</section>

	<section id="why">
		<h2>Why Choose QuickRichClub?</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<article>
					<picture>
						<Icon name="uil:bitcoin-circle" title="" />
					</picture>
					<header>
						<h3>Unbelievable Returns</h3>
					</header>
					<p>No, seriously, you'd better not believe them.</p>
				</article>
			</li>
			<li>
				<article>
					<picture>
						<Icon name="uil:brain" title="" />
					</picture>
					<header>
						<h3>Team-Building Extravaganza</h3>
					</header>
					<p>
						Convince your loved ones to join in and put the <span class="fun-text">"fun"</span>
						<span class="fun-text">"generational debt"</span>!
					</p>
				</article>
			</li>
			<li>
				<article>
					<picture>
						<Icon name="uil:fire" title="" />
					</picture>
					<header>
						<h3>Risk-Free!</h3>
					</header>
					<p>For us, anyway. For you, well, that's another story.</p>
				</article>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section id="steps">
		<h2>How It "Works"?</h2>

		<p>You will be done in only 3 easy steps!</p>

		<ol>
			<li>
				<h3>Join</h3>
				<p>Hand over your hard-earned cash because why not?</p>
				<p><small class="tiny-text">(This is not a threat)</small></p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h3>Recruit</h3>
				<p>Annoy your friends and family until they give in.</p>
				<p>Remember, the more they invest, the more... well, that's it.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h3>Profit?!?</h3>
				<p>Watch as your money magically does absolutely nothing.</p>
				<p>It's like a miracle, but not the good kind.</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
	</section>

	<section id="testimonials">
		<h2>Testimonials</h2>

		<ul>
			<li>
				<blockquote>
					<Image
						src={customer}
						alt=""
						loading="lazy"
						widths={[128, 256, 512, 768, customer.width]}
						sizes={`(max-width: 360px) 128px, (max-width: 720px) 256px, (max-width: 1280px) 512px, (max-width: 2160px) 768px ${customer.width}px`}
						quality={75}
					/>
					<p>QuickRichClub changed my life! Now I have plenty of free time because everyone I know avoids me!</p>
					<small>A Truly "Satisfied" Member</small>
				</blockquote>
			</li>
			<li>
				<blockquote>
					<Image
						src={ligMa}
						alt=""
						loading="lazy"
						widths={[128, 256, 512, 768, ligMa.width]}
						sizes={`(max-width: 360px) 128px, (max-width: 720px) 256px, (max-width: 1280px) 512px, (max-width: 2160px) 768px ${ligMa.width}px`}
						quality={75}
					/>
					<p>I was skeptical, but now I'm a full believer... in never falling for these schemes again!</p>
					<small>Lig Ma B.</small>
				</blockquote>
			</li>
			<li>
				<blockquote>
					<Image
						src={eMusk}
						alt=""
						loading="lazy"
						widths={[128, 256, 512, 768, eMusk.width]}
						sizes={`(max-width: 360px) 128px, (max-width: 720px) 256px, (max-width: 1280px) 512px, (max-width: 2160px) 768px ${eMusk.width}px`}
						quality={75}
					/>
					<p>I've never had so many people call me about investment opportunities... mainly to tell me to stop calling them.</p>
					<small>E. Musk</small>
				</blockquote>
			</li>
			<li>
				<blockquote>
					<Image
						src={mScott}
						alt=""
						loading="lazy"
						widths={[128, 256, 512, 768, mScott.width]}
						sizes={`(max-width: 360px) 128px, (max-width: 720px) 256px, (max-width: 1280px) 512px, (max-width: 2160px) 768px ${mScott.width}px`}
						quality={75}
					/>
					<p>This is totally <em>not</em> a pyramid scheme!</p>
					<small>M. Scott</small>
				</blockquote>
			</li>
			<li>
				<blockquote>
					<Image
						src={mrCreature}
						alt=""
						loading="lazy"
						widths={[128, 256, 512, 768, mrCreature.width]}
						sizes={`(max-width: 360px) 128px, (max-width: 720px) 256px, (max-width: 1280px) 512px, (max-width: 2160px) 768px ${mrCreature.width}px`}
						quality={75}
					/>
					<p>Thanks to QuickRichClub, I learned a valuable lesson in financial caution. Also, my friends learned how to block numbers.</p>
					<small>Mr. Creature</small>
				</blockquote>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section id="cta">
		<h2>Act Now!</h2>

		<p>Sign up today and experience the thrill of watching your money disappear! Join QuickRichClub &mdash; the not-a-pyramid scheme that might make someone rich!</p>
		<p><small class="tiny-text">(spoiler: it's not you)</small></p>

		<form method="get" action="#">
			<input
				id="email"
				name="email"
				type="email"
				placeholder="Enter your email here"
				aria-label="Your email"
				required
			/>
			<button type="submit">Access now!</button>
		</form>
	</section>

	<p slot="footer" id="small-print">By providing your email you subscribe to a lifetime suply of Sildenafil, also known as "Magic Blue Pills" or "Daddy Little Helpers".</p>
	<script src="../assets/js/pages/triangle.ts"></script>
</BaseLayout>
